TYPESCRIPT STANDARDS
Rule Example All request/response shapes in `lib/types.ts` `import type { AgentConfig } from '@/lib/types'` No implicit `any` `const data: unknown = await res.json()` then narrow Use `type` not `interface` for simple shapes `type ApiResponse = { items: Item[] }` Discriminated unions for status types `type Status = 'pending' \ 'done' \ 'error'` Explicit return types on exported functions `export async function getVenture(): Promise<Venture>` 
